The directory structure of this particular project is:
├── build
│   ├── executable
├── Makefile
├── module1
│   ├── build
│   │   └── README
│   ├── includes
│   │   └── *.h
│   ├── Makefile
│   └── src
│       └── *.cpp
├── module2
│   ├── build
│   │   └── README
│   ├── includes
│   │   └── *.h
│   ├── Makefile
│   └── src
│       └── *.cpp
└── README

The top level Makefile calls recursively lover lever Makefiles in order to clean/build the application binaries.
